profile:
www.lorisdawn.com

Unique custom lighting: chandeliers, pendants, mini-pendants, table lamps, floor lamps, illuminated art to enhance your living space. Contemporary, Art deco and Victorian styles created with a new twist. Modern lighting, yet reminiscent of Tiffany lighting. Loris also creates window panels with an ornate style of twisting wire, similar to window grates of days past. Hand-made, no two pieces of her art are ever the same.
